<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#947721">{قَاتِلُوهُمْ يُعَذِّبْهُمُ اللَّهُ بِأَيْدِيكُمْ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[التوبة: ١٤]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
